You are using the variable **idCall** in your fetch call when there is no such defined variable in your code.

wixData.get() requires an item id to retrieve the item.

On top of that you cannot send the entire item in the url. you need to specify which field key you want to use. such as **id.fieldKey**

Your code should be like

    let id = await wixData.get(&#39;#myDatabaseName&#39;, itemId);

    const response = fetch(&quot;https://www.exampleapi.com/data/d5/feed?&amp;id=&quot; + id.fieldKey + &quot;&amp;key=&quot; + apiKey, {
    method: &#39;get&#39; });

